







Lanes Group plc

















































































Taking drainage and wastewater to another level
 


SCROLL DOWN





Taking drainage and wastewater to another level
 











Lanes Group is the leading wastewater utility solutions provider and largest independent drainage specialist in the UK, with turnover in excess of £165 million.We have three operating brands, three divisions dedicated to specific market sectors, and a network of centres across the UK and Eire.Our customers range from householders to large utility companies, and everyone in between.Welcome to the Lanes Group.










Built on principles
 







Built on principles
 




























Lanes Group provides 24/7 response to drainage emergencies; drainage maintenance, rehabilitation and renewal; consultancy and waste management services.What began as a Leeds-based drainage company is now firmly established at the pinnacle of the drainage sector, employing some 1900 people in the UK and Eire.We believe that our success is based on a pioneering spirit, a solid growth strategy and a robust infrastructure. Our policy is to expand in existing, and new, markets, whilst maintaining the ethos upon which we have built the business.Our commitment to product innovation, customer service and the health, safety and well being of our people and the public form the cornerstones of the Lanes Group operation. And that is how we intend to continue – long into the future.Investing today for tomorrow.










Our businesses
 







Our businesses
 











Wherever you go in the Lanes Group, you will find the ethos of service, safety and excellence evident in everything we do.We work hard to ensure that everyone who represents our Group cares as much as we do.To understand more about our operating brands and specialist divisions, please see the individual pages.Lanes’ business, Lanes’ standardsOur Businesses



















































Services & sectors
 







Services & sectors
 



















Lanes Group offers a complete A to Z of drainage services to all markets and all sectors of the market, including:domesticindustrialcommercialretailblue chiputilityrailhighwaysnuclearmanufacturinginsuranceClients benefit from the strength which comes from this diversity. Specialist sectors may require that our services are delivered in a different way but, whether we are servicing a huge utility framework contract, rehabilitating kilometres of public sewers or unblocking a domestic drain, one thing is always the same — customer care.  Lanes’ clients expect nothing less. 













 




