24/7 responses to drainage emergencies with removal, rehabilitation and renewal, as well as consultancy and waste management systems



An industry leader with nationwide coverage and roughly 1900 staff in the UK and Ireland



A sizeable, stable operation turning over more than £150m each year









Lanes Group provides 24/7 responses to drainage emergencies with removal, rehabilitation and renewal, as well as consultancy and waste management services. What began as a Leeds-based drainage company is now firmly established as an industry leader, with turnover in excess of £150 million and roughly 1900 staff in the UK and Ireland.




We believe that our success is based on a pioneering spirit, solid growth strategy and robust infrastructure. Our commitment to product innovation, customer service and the health, safety and wellbeing of our people and the public form the cornerstones of our operations, and will continue to do so for years to come.



























